Cc: Philipp Zabel <p.zabel@pengutronix.de>
Reviewed-by: Nishanth Menon <nm@ti.com>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20221030055636.3139-1-rdunlap@infradead.org
Signed-off-by: Philipp Zabel <p.zabel@pengutronix.de>
